{"tid":2265613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"831血腥鎮壓14個月 有市民太子站附近被指違限聚令遭警票控","createTime":"2020-10-31T14:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T15:22:12.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b54c131c516db34af6641ecf0532b75faadf230f","tid":2265613,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T14:47:33.000Z","msg":"831事件14個月 有市民太子站附近被指違限聚令遭警票控<br />\n<br />\n831太子站事件14個月，多名軍裝警員傍晚起在太子站一帶戒備，在B1出口外拉起橙帶圍封部分區域。有市民帶備鮮花擺放在出口外，數名油尖旺區議員亦在出口外接收鮮花。警方曾以擴音器警告現場人士已違反限聚令，又在西洋菜街截查市民。有市民表示，被警方指違反限聚令而發出告票。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2364144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2364144&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=841a0ac2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2364144</a>"},{"pid":"034814e5bb6ef2fd83937c49bdd7db39b0a92f99","tid":2265613,"uid":113000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T14:48:20.000Z","msg":"多人地方唔告<br />\n<br />\n唔係政治打壓都冇人信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad846dde58a4aa5e28ebc6486bd32ee195017224","tid":2265613,"uid":298225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"034814e5bb6ef2fd83937c49bdd7db39b0a92f99","tid":2265613,"uid":113000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T14:48:20.000Z","msg":"多人地方唔告<br />\n<br />\n唔係政治打壓都冇人信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T14:49:41.000Z","msg":"去老蘭今晚發達啦，全撚部$2000"},{"pid":"46d1f7cc24dda23ca79edd6be3cecaa892fe4428","tid":2265613,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad846dde58a4aa5e28ebc6486bd32ee195017224","tid":2265613,"uid":298225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"034814e5bb6ef2fd83937c49bdd7db39b0a92f99","tid":2265613,"uid":113000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T14:48:20.000Z","msg":"多人地方唔告<br